### update item
PATCH {{url}}/api/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Antyk3",
    "isMagic": true,
    "type": "bron",
    "weaponType": "miecz",
    "weaponBalance": 13
}

### delete item
DELETE {{url}}/api/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

